question: What will be the Federal Funds Target Rate (Upper Bound) after the Jan 2026 FOMC?
description: Predict the upper limit of the Federal Funds Target Range announced at the conclusion of the Jan 28, 2026 FOMC meeting.
resolutionCriteria:
Resolves to the Upper Bound of the target range in the Implementation Note.
- Date: Jan 28, 2026.
- Hard Lock: 1:00 PM ET (1 hour before announcement).
- Value: 450 bps = 4.50%.
